    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the \"balanced\" thing but the problem is that wind and solar are so intermittent. if we try to rely on them too much we might actually make things worse or just fail to hit our targets. isn't it actually more dangerous to gamble on renewables when we have a proven high-output option like nuclear sitting right there?",
